  Item 8.01 Other Events.                     
                                              
On June 28, 2023, the Corporate Governance and
Nominating Committee of the Board of Directors
(Board) of The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc. (the 
Registrant) recommended that the Board take   
action at its next upcoming meeting to appoint
Thomas K. Montag as an independent member of  
the Registrant’s Board and each of its Audit, 
Risk and Corporate Governance and Nominating  
Committees. Such appointment would take effect
if and when the Board takes action to approve 
it.
